\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0  He could see ill omens in the darting flight of a black bird. Blabh blah blah. Or, as now, in the body of a boy under a bush.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 This was a strange coincidence because he was about to hide up under this bush. That there was a dead body already there - freshly dead by the look of him - well that was a strange coincidence indeed.}
